in a special situation

293
00:10:48,100 --> 00:10:49,360
and needs it urgently.

294
00:10:49,810 --> 00:10:50,570
Yes.

295
00:10:51,670 --> 00:10:53,790
Come on, Renyu!
Why are you being so fussy?

296
00:10:53,790 --> 00:10:56,720
Don't you keep
your HSBC clients confidential, too?

297
00:10:56,790 --> 00:10:58,240
Besides, last night

298
00:10:58,340 --> 00:11:00,000
when I mentioned Mr. He to you,

299
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:00,860
you told me

300
00:11:00,860 --> 00:11:02,050
how amazing he was

301
00:11:02,050 --> 00:11:03,530
and that you wanted to meet him.

302
00:11:03,530 --> 00:11:04,930
