448
00:14:57,740 --> 00:14:59,050
who this client is

449
00:14:59,050 --> 00:15:00,910
and what these US dollars are for.

450
00:15:01,450 --> 00:15:02,190
I'm sorry.

451
00:15:02,860 --> 00:15:05,150
I've promised my client to keep it secret.

452
00:15:05,150 --> 00:15:06,080
I can't tell you.

453
00:15:06,190 --> 00:15:08,190
Listen to him making excuses!

454
00:15:08,190 --> 00:15:09,150
Just tell us!

455
00:15:09,150 --> 00:15:09,410
Yeah!

456
00:15:09,410 --> 00:15:10,050
Don't be silent!

457
00:15:10,050 --> 00:15:10,390
Say it!

458
00:15:10,390 --> 00:15:11,320
Enough.

459
00:15:11,580 --> 00:15:12,410
Stop it!

460
00:15:15,700 --> 00:15:16,550
He Xian,

461
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:19,670
on behalf of everyone,
I'll ask you one last time.

462
00:15:19,670 --> 00:15:21,400
Can you return these US dollars

463
00:15:22,010 --> 00:15:22,930
or not?

464
00:15:26,220 --> 00:15:26,950
Lyu,

465
00:15:27,190 --> 00:15:29,250
if I've caused any losses for anyone,

466
00:15:29,650 --> 00:15:30,950
I can offer nothing but my apologies.

467
00:15:30,950 --> 00:15:32,410
Is this how you do business?

468
00:15:32,410 --> 00:15:32,690
You're

469
00:15:32,690 --> 00:15:33,690
