546
00:19:52,540 --> 00:19:54,830
what I have to do to get paid.

547
00:19:55,040 --> 00:19:56,440
I'm more concerned about

548
00:19:56,760 --> 00:20:00,090
the dozens of cases
of precision instruments and medicine.

549
00:20:00,260 --> 00:20:02,950
