563
00:20:26,170 --> 00:20:28,830
If you want the money
for the previous shipment,

564
00:20:28,870 --> 00:20:29,930
you must promise me

565
00:20:30,760 --> 00:20:33,290
not to sell this new shipment
to the Japanese.

566
00:20:37,040 --> 00:20:39,280
Fine, I won't do that, okay?

567
00:20:42,540 --> 00:20:44,630
Can you guarantee I'll get paid?

568
00:20:55,260 --> 00:20:57,390
Whether or not those U.S. dollar bills

569
00:20:57,590 --> 00:20:59,120
are intact or retrievable,

570
00:20:59,130 --> 00:21:01,300
as long as you keep the goods
from the Japanese,

571
00:21:01,300 --> 00:21:03,200
I'll see to it that you get paid.

572
00:21:03,830 --> 00:21:05,890
When the bills are recovered, I'll pay up.

573
00:21:05,890 --> 00:21:07,290
If they're forever lost,

574
00:21:07,560 --> 00:21:08,930
I'll put all my assets for sale,

575
00:21:08,930 --> 00:21:10,980
including my house and land,
or borrow from loan sharks

576
00:21:10,980 --> 00:21:13,130
to make sure you receive
every penny you deserve.

577
00:21:13,130 --> 00:21:15,390
But if you sell the goods to the Japanese,

578
00:21:17,700 --> 00:21:19,630
don't blame me for refusing to pay.

579
00:21:26,170 --> 00:21:27,000
Xian?

580
00:21:27,760 --> 00:21:28,960
You're finally back.

581
00:21:29,930 --> 00:21:30,740
Sit down.

582
00:21:31,830 --> 00:21:32,830
Let me take a look.

583
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:40,150
Did you get injured?

584
00:21:41,040 --> 00:21:41,690
I'm fine.

585
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:43,330
Are you really fine?

586
00:21:43,500 --> 00:21:44,390
Yes, I am fine.

587
00:21:49,930 --> 00:21:50,600
When

588
00:21:50,930 --> 00:21:53,060
Quan brought those U.S. dollars back,

589
00:21:53,350 --> 00:21:55,550
he told me that Huilong Bank
was bombed.

590
00:21:55,910 --> 00:21:57,640
I was frightened out of my wits.

591
00:21:58,350 --> 00:22:00,090
Yet you dashed into it
despite the explosion.

592
00:22:00,090 --> 00:22:01,950
Please don't do that again, okay?

593
00:22:02,560 --> 00:22:04,890
What can be more important than your life?

594
00:22:05,780 --> 00:22:06,700
Don't worry.

595
00:22:10,200 --> 00:22:12,060
Where's that box of U.S. dollars?

596
00:22:12,260 --> 00:22:13,260
Father has it now.

597
00:22:16,910 --> 00:22:17,800
Wait.

598
00:22:19,010 --> 00:22:19,670
Father

599
00:22:19,700 --> 00:22:21,630
heard some gossip about you.

600
00:22:22,390 --> 00:22:23,390
He's a bit upset.

601
00:22:26,540 --> 00:22:27,390
I get it.

602
00:22:36,910 --> 00:22:38,000
There are...

603
00:22:39,140 --> 00:22:39,640
six.

604
00:22:39,670 --> 00:22:40,480
Right, six.

605
00:22:40,480 --> 00:22:41,090
Note it down.

606
00:22:41,090 --> 00:22:41,540
Okay.

607
00:22:44,500 --> 00:22:45,000
Renyu.

608
00:22:46,300 --> 00:22:46,780
Sir.

609
00:22:47,260 --> 00:22:48,920
Why are you home so late today?

610
00:22:49,330 --> 00:22:50,850
There was a run on the bank
the entire day.

611
00:22:50,850 --> 00:22:53,040
People formed a line
that stretched over a kilometer.

612
00:22:53,040 --> 00:22:54,350
Due to lack of manpower,

613
00:22:54,350 --> 00:22:55,810
I had to work till just now.

614
00:22:57,020 --> 00:22:57,550
Mr. Heng,

615
00:22:57,930 --> 00:22:59,390
I can handle the rest myself.

616
00:22:59,390 --> 00:23:00,480
Go get some rest now.

617
00:23:00,480 --> 00:23:01,390
Okay, got it.

618
00:23:01,980 --> 00:23:02,670
I'll be going then.

619
00:23:02,670 --> 00:23:03,200
Okay.

620
00:23:05,330 --> 00:23:06,390
What are you doing?

621
00:23:07,390 --> 00:23:09,540
The orphanage has taken in
many refugee children.

622
00:23:09,540 --> 00:23:11,260
The housemother
said they were out of food.

623
00:23:11,260 --> 00:23:13,520
I plan to send
what we have at home to them.

624
00:23:14,240 --> 00:23:15,460
But these...

625
00:23:15,460 --> 00:23:17,260
can only last them for a few days.

626
00:23:18,390 --> 00:23:18,890
Renyu,

627
00:23:20,500 --> 00:23:21,910
is there any money on you?

628
00:23:24,950 --> 00:23:26,300
The bank has imposed withdrawal limits.

629
00:23:26,300 --> 00:23:27,150
Each person

630
00:23:27,410 --> 00:23:29,610
can only withdraw 100 Hong Kong dollars.

631
00:23:29,610 --> 00:23:31,520
I can't access my funds either.

632
00:23:32,410 --> 00:23:33,410
Use it sparingly.

633
00:23:34,630 --> 00:23:35,090
Okay.

634
00:23:48,610 --> 00:23:49,200
Father,

635
00:23:49,930 --> 00:23:50,700
I'm back.

636
00:24:09,500 --> 00:24:10,240
Father...

637
00:24:13,520 --> 00:24:14,190
Kneel.

638
00:24:39,560 --> 00:24:41,260
Before our ancestors,

639
00:24:41,540 --> 00:24:42,950
answer truthfully.

640
00:24:44,300 --> 00:24:44,930
Yes.

641
00:24:45,670 --> 00:24:46,870
Throughout this day,

642
00:24:47,630 --> 00:24:50,020
did you engage in dishonest conduct
in business?

643
00:24:50,020 --> 00:24:50,980
No.

644
00:24:51,390 --> 00:24:52,190
Did you

645
00:24:52,390 --> 00:24:53,540
break any promises?

646
00:24:54,040 --> 00:24:55,130
No.

647
00:24:55,800 --> 00:24:58,950
In any other thing you did,
did you live up to

648
00:24:58,950 --> 00:25:00,410
the teachings of our ancestors

649
00:25:00,410 --> 00:25:02,000
and act with a clear conscience?

650
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:03,460
I, He Xian, swear that I haven't done

651
00:25:03,460 --> 00:25:05,000
anything deviated from my duty.

652
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:05,930
My conscience remains clear.

653
00:25:05,930 --> 00:25:07,280
Nonsense!

654
00:25:07,280 --> 00:25:09,930
How dare you lie before our ancestors!

655
00:25:09,930 --> 00:25:11,390
I'll beat you to death, you dishonorable

656
00:25:11,390 --> 00:25:12,740
disgrace to the family!

657
00:25:17,870 --> 00:25:19,350
Father, Father!

658
00:25:21,040 --> 00:25:21,910
Let go!

659
00:25:23,450 --> 00:25:25,280
On... your knees.

660
00:25:28,830 --> 00:25:29,800
Kneel!

661
00:25:34,200 --> 00:25:34,980
Tell me.

662
00:25:35,450 --> 00:25:37,110
What got into you and drove you

663
00:25:37,850 --> 00:25:39,330
to scam your industry peers

664
00:25:39,330 --> 00:25:40,300
for

665
00:25:41,200 --> 00:25:42,370
filthy lucre?

666
00:25:43,150 --> 00:25:43,890
I didn't.

667
00:25:45,540 --> 00:25:47,170
How dare you deny it.

668
00:25:47,170 --> 00:25:48,460
What you've done

669
00:25:49,450 --> 00:25:51,710
has become the talk of the neighborhood.

670
00:25:52,020 --> 00:25:53,370
Now, outside,

671
00:25:53,370 --> 00:25:56,460
everyone is pointing fingers
at the He family!

672
00:25:57,060 --> 00:25:59,090
Are all these people

673
00:25:59,090 --> 00:26:01,000
falsely accusing you?

674
00:26:01,000 --> 00:26:01,800
And...

675
00:26:02,590 --> 00:26:03,650
What's in this box?

676
00:26:06,800 --> 00:26:08,400
U.S. dollars I got exchanged

677
00:26:08,450 --> 00:26:09,290
for a client.

678
00:26:11,610 --> 00:26:12,300
Client?

679
00:26:13,170 --> 00:26:13,900
What client?

680
00:26:16,780 --> 00:26:18,640
I promised him confidentiality,

681
00:26:19,150 --> 00:26:20,010
so I can't tell.

682
00:26:21,870 --> 00:26:23,240
Not even to me?

683
00:26:25,460 --> 00:26:25,890
No.

684
00:26:31,220 --> 00:26:31,890
You...

685
00:26:32,670 --> 00:26:33,650
Go on.

686
00:26:35,540 --> 00:26:36,150
Father,

687
00:26:37,040 --> 00:26:38,760
by exchanging currency
for a client this time,

688
00:26:38,760 --> 00:26:41,090
I did cause losses to some industry peers.

689
00:26:41,390 --> 00:26:43,190
But it was purely coincidental.

690
00:26:43,610 --> 00:26:44,760
I had no prior knowledge

691
00:26:44,760 --> 00:26:46,560
of Japan's attacks at Hong Kong.

692
00:26:47,090 --> 00:26:47,800
Besides,

693
00:26:47,800 --> 00:26:48,850
I can guarantee

694
00:26:49,040 --> 00:26:51,370
this client is a legitimate businessman.

695
00:26:51,370 --> 00:26:54,220
He had a valid reason
for this urgent exchange of currency.

696
00:26:54,220 --> 00:26:55,780
And this business deal of his

697
00:26:55,780 --> 00:26:57,710
is related to national interests.

698
00:26:58,330 --> 00:26:59,390
Therefore, I had to

699
00:26:59,720 --> 00:27:01,050
do my utmost to help him.

700
00:27:04,610 --> 00:27:05,350
Are you...

701
00:27:06,540 --> 00:27:07,600
telling the truth?

702
00:27:08,350 --> 00:27:09,460
I swear to you

703
00:27:09,460 --> 00:27:10,560
and our ancestors

704
00:27:10,960 --> 00:27:12,490
that every word I've spoken

705
00:27:12,500 --> 00:27:13,630
is absolutely true.

706
00:27:17,930 --> 00:27:19,460
I'll believe you this time.

707
00:27:20,650 --> 00:27:21,650
Get up.

708
00:27:31,500 --> 00:27:33,100
But I have one more question.

709
00:27:33,520 --> 00:27:35,250
You got this box of U.S. dollars

710
00:27:35,350 --> 00:27:37,430
exchanged for a client.

711
00:27:37,890 --> 00:27:39,280
It was so important an issue

712
00:27:39,280 --> 00:27:40,780
that no mistake was allowed.

713
00:27:40,780 --> 00:27:42,720
You did the right thing

714
00:27:42,720 --> 00:27:44,850
by risking your life to bring this box

715
00:27:45,200 --> 00:27:46,260
out of flames.

716
00:27:46,260 --> 00:27:47,980
But why did you rush

717
00:27:47,980 --> 00:27:50,060
back into the fire again afterwards?

718
00:27:50,060 --> 00:27:51,390
Did you care that much about

719
00:27:51,390 --> 00:27:53,320
those measly possessions inside?

720
00:27:53,590 --> 00:27:55,260
You're head of our family.

721
00:27:56,450 --> 00:27:58,310
If something had happened to you,

722
00:27:58,690 --> 00:28:01,040
how would that leave Qiwen

723
00:28:01,040 --> 00:28:02,100
and the children?

724
00:28:05,460 --> 00:28:06,110
Father,

725
00:28:07,460 --> 00:28:10,040
I know I made a very risky move.

726
00:28:10,330 --> 00:28:11,390
But at that moment,

727
00:28:11,430 --> 00:28:13,500
I had no choice
but to go back into the fire,

728
00:28:13,500 --> 00:28:15,630
because this ledger must be preserved

729
00:28:18,020 --> 00:28:19,480
under all circumstances.

730
00:28:29,700 --> 00:28:30,450
Huilong's record of deposit accounts?

731
00:28:30,450 --> 00:28:32,500
[Deposit Accounts]

732
00:28:32,500 --> 00:28:33,150
Yes.

733
00:28:33,870 --> 00:28:35,330
Huilong is a small bank.

734
00:28:36,110 --> 00:28:37,480
Those who deposit money with us

735
00:28:37,480 --> 00:28:39,010
are mostly ordinary people

736
00:28:39,090 --> 00:28:40,240
of modest means.

737
00:28:40,560 --> 00:28:42,510
They entrust their hard-earned money

738
00:28:42,510 --> 00:28:42,610
[Li Tianyou deposited 120 dollars]
[Zhao Xuebao deposited 20 dollars]

739
00:28:42,610 --> 00:28:43,650
to Huilong for my management

740
00:28:43,650 --> 00:28:44,950
and interest earnings,

741
00:28:44,950 --> 00:28:46,370
which shows complete trust

742
00:28:46,370 --> 00:28:47,450
in me and Huilong.

743
00:28:47,690 --> 00:28:49,470
Now, with Hong Kong in crisis,

744
00:28:49,740 --> 00:28:51,460
everyone lives in uncertainty.

745
00:28:51,460 --> 00:28:52,300
These deposits

746
00:28:52,300 --> 00:28:54,760
could be life-saving money
for many of them.

747
00:28:54,800 --> 00:28:57,400
I must ensure
they don't lose all their assets.

748
00:29:06,650 --> 00:29:07,300
Xian,

749
00:29:11,520 --> 00:29:12,300
you made

750
00:29:13,280 --> 00:29:14,450
the right choice.

751
00:29:16,320 --> 00:29:17,960
What do you plan to do next?

752
00:29:20,690 --> 00:29:21,690
I will, of course,

753
00:29:22,020 --> 00:29:23,000
raise funds

754
00:29:23,260 --> 00:29:25,660
and prepare cash for deposit withdrawals.

755
00:29:25,950 --> 00:29:26,800
But now,

756
00:29:26,800 --> 00:29:28,700
all the cash in Huilong has been burned.

757
00:29:28,700 --> 00:29:30,390
All trading has been suspended
on both the stock exchange

758
00:29:30,390 --> 00:29:32,190
and the currency exchange due to war.

759
00:29:32,190 --> 00:29:34,870
I can't cash the investments
made for the clients.

760
00:29:34,870 --> 00:29:36,700
As for the money
we lent to our industry peers,

761
00:29:36,700 --> 00:29:38,430
I failed to get even a penny back

762
00:29:38,450 --> 00:29:39,980
after a whole day of trying.

763
00:29:43,610 --> 00:29:44,190
Tell me.

764
00:29:44,650 --> 00:29:46,310
How much money do you need now?

765
00:29:46,800 --> 00:29:48,200
I did some rough calculations.

766
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:49,200
If I sell the house

767
00:29:49,780 --> 00:29:51,580
and put together all I can offer,

768
00:29:52,000 --> 00:29:54,400
only 40% of the deposits can be paid out.

769
00:29:56,300 --> 00:29:57,630
That's far from enough.

770
00:30:03,170 --> 00:30:05,430
I'd hate to let the depositors
suffer losses.

771
00:30:05,430 --> 00:30:06,110
So,

772
00:30:06,960 --> 00:30:08,130
I'll raise as many funds

773
00:30:08,130 --> 00:30:11,060
as possible to pay out
the deposits proportionally.

774
00:30:11,800 --> 00:30:12,460
All I ask for

775
00:30:13,060 --> 00:30:14,320
is a clear conscience.

776
00:30:15,460 --> 00:30:16,260
I understand.

777
00:30:18,500 --> 00:30:19,500
You may leave now.

778
00:30:41,740 --> 00:30:42,390
Qiwen,

779
00:30:43,830 --> 00:30:45,030
I want a word with you.

780
00:30:47,800 --> 00:30:48,330
No need.

781
00:30:50,060 --> 00:30:51,860
I heard what you and Father said.

782
00:30:52,390 --> 00:30:53,060
Just do

783
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:56,060
whatever you set your mind to.

784
00:30:57,020 --> 00:30:58,280
No need to ask me at all.

785
00:30:59,930 --> 00:31:00,720
I'm sorry.

786
00:31:01,980 --> 00:31:02,720
From now on,

787
00:31:03,520 --> 00:31:05,320
I'm afraid you'll be put through

788
00:31:05,370 --> 00:31:06,630
some lean days with me.

789
00:31:07,390 --> 00:31:08,790
What kind of talk is that?

790
00:31:09,520 --> 00:31:10,850
We're husband and wife.

791
00:31:11,410 --> 00:31:14,810
Of course we'll weather through
all difficulties together.

792
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:17,260
Don't worry.

793
00:31:18,200 --> 00:31:19,260
I'm here to take care of the family,

794
00:31:19,260 --> 00:31:19,790
alright?

795
00:31:22,200 --> 00:31:23,530
We'll get through this.

796
00:31:36,240 --> 00:31:36,830
Father.

797
00:31:37,980 --> 00:31:38,690
Father.

798
00:31:45,330 --> 00:31:46,300
Here is

799
00:31:46,850 --> 00:31:48,800
everything I own.

800
00:31:50,610 --> 00:31:50,680
Take a look.

801
00:31:50,680 --> 00:31:51,560
[Buyer: He Chengxi]
[Deposit]

802
00:31:51,560 --> 00:31:52,820
See if they're enough.

803
00:31:53,370 --> 00:31:54,890
You worked your entire life for these.

804
00:31:54,890 --> 00:31:56,550
You need them for your old age.

805
00:31:56,910 --> 00:31:57,970
I can't take these.

806
00:31:58,960 --> 00:32:00,490
The He family's reputation

807
00:32:00,960 --> 00:32:03,000
matters more than me, an old man.

808
00:32:05,110 --> 00:32:05,890
Xian,

809
00:32:06,890 --> 00:32:07,560
sit down.

810
00:32:23,520 --> 00:32:24,720
Father, let me do it.

811
00:32:36,330 --> 00:32:37,990
It's fine to lose the business

812
00:32:39,170 --> 00:32:40,960
and close the money changer.

813
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:43,850
But we must keep...

814
00:32:45,460 --> 00:32:46,590
a clear conscience.

815
00:32:47,910 --> 00:32:49,190
I'm already

816
00:32:49,700 --> 00:32:51,760
a man with one foot in the grave.

817
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:56,540
What's the use of keeping all this money?

818
00:32:57,480 --> 00:33:00,460
It will eventually go to my descendants.

819
00:33:01,870 --> 00:33:04,070
As long as they learn to be honest people

820
00:33:05,330 --> 00:33:06,720
of integrity,

821
00:33:08,590 --> 00:33:09,720
what does it matter

822
00:33:10,560 --> 00:33:12,110
if they have money or not?

823
00:33:13,410 --> 00:33:16,500
Spending all this
on maintaining a clear conscience

824
00:33:16,850 --> 00:33:19,180
is more worthwhile than on anything else.

825
00:33:23,040 --> 00:33:23,700
Father.

826
00:33:29,850 --> 00:33:30,410
Mr. Lyu,

827
00:33:30,850 --> 00:33:32,930
why do you only pay out 20% of my deposit?

828
00:33:32,930 --> 00:33:34,860
Why can't I withdraw more than 15%?

829
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:35,800
Yeah!

830
00:33:37,930 --> 00:33:38,650
Mr. Lyu,

831
00:33:39,190 --> 00:33:40,610
I need to withdraw my deposit!

832
00:33:40,610 --> 00:33:41,890
I'm trying to survive!

833
00:33:41,890 --> 00:33:43,150
I can't go on with my life this way!

834
00:33:43,150 --> 00:33:43,890
Mr. Lyu!

835
00:33:44,520 --> 00:33:46,370
-This won't do!
-Give us our money back!

836
00:33:46,370 --> 00:33:48,470
When will you pay out my deposit?

837
00:33:48,690 --> 00:33:49,410
Pay up!

838
00:33:49,430 --> 00:33:50,060
Pay up!

839
00:33:50,540 --> 00:33:52,060
Give our money back to us!

840
00:34:19,250 --> 00:34:20,330
There are still people here?

841
00:34:20,330 --> 00:34:21,730
Withdrawals available?

842
00:34:24,500 --> 00:34:25,159
Mr. He,

843
00:34:25,710 --> 00:34:28,239
can we really make withdrawals
from Huilong?

844
00:34:28,560 --> 00:34:29,310
Yes, you can.

845
00:34:29,560 --> 00:34:31,429
What's the percentage?

846
00:34:32,620 --> 00:34:34,540
One hundred,
when you show you deposit slip.

847
00:34:34,540 --> 00:34:36,290
Do you have your deposit slip now?

848
00:34:36,290 --> 00:34:37,139
Yes, I do.

849
00:34:38,330 --> 00:34:38,960
Careful.

850
00:34:41,830 --> 00:34:42,290
Quan,

851
00:34:42,830 --> 00:34:44,330
it's 567.54 dollars.

852
00:34:44,330 --> 00:34:44,870
Got it.

853
00:34:51,730 --> 00:34:53,350
Sir, count it.

854
00:34:57,100 --> 00:34:57,600
Correct?

855
00:34:57,600 --> 00:34:58,130
Correct.

856
00:34:58,640 --> 00:34:59,570
Correct amount.

857
00:35:00,270 --> 00:35:02,270
I'll close your account then.

858
00:35:03,460 --> 00:35:05,590
I didn't expect to get this money back.

859
00:35:06,140 --> 00:35:07,540
It's even in full amount.

860
00:35:07,730 --> 00:35:09,750
Thank you.

861
00:35:09,750 --> 00:35:10,640
Take care.

862
00:35:10,740 --> 00:35:12,940
[Huilong Bank will shut down
due to war]

863
00:35:12,940 --> 00:35:13,820
[Withdraw your deposits
with certificates
and close accounts in 15 days]

864
00:35:13,820 --> 00:35:15,310
Withdrawals are really available?

865
00:35:15,310 --> 00:35:16,270
In full amount, too!

866
00:35:16,270 --> 00:35:16,540
Yeah.

867
00:35:16,540 --> 00:35:19,000
I wish I had deposited my money
with Huilong.

868
00:35:19,520 --> 00:35:20,100
Sir,

869
00:35:20,270 --> 00:35:21,480
when is the last day of business?

870
00:35:21,480 --> 00:35:23,080
My neighbor
is also a depositor of Huillong.

871
00:35:23,080 --> 00:35:24,070
I need to tell him about this!

872
00:35:24,070 --> 00:35:24,560
[Huilong Bank will shut down
due to war]

873
00:35:24,560 --> 00:35:25,620
Starting today,

874
00:35:25,620 --> 00:35:26,160
in each of the next 15 days,

875
00:35:26,160 --> 00:35:26,560
[Withdraw your deposits
with certificates
and close accounts in 15 days]

876
00:35:26,560 --> 00:35:28,430
Huilong Bank will be open till 6 p.m.

877
00:35:28,430 --> 00:35:29,760
Please spread the word,

878
00:35:29,870 --> 00:35:31,520
make withdrawals,
and close accounts in time.

879
00:35:31,520 --> 00:35:32,600
Hey, sir!

880
00:35:32,600 --> 00:35:33,080
Here's my deposit slip!

881
00:35:33,080 --> 00:35:33,680
Don't rush.

882
00:35:33,680 --> 00:35:34,390
Here's mine!

883
00:35:34,390 --> 00:35:35,960
-I'm also a depositor of Huilong!
-Please don't rush.

884
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:36,910
One client at a time.

885
00:35:36,910 --> 00:35:37,640
We guarantee full payment.

886
00:35:37,640 --> 00:35:39,060
-Don't rush.
-Line up, please.

887
00:35:39,060 --> 00:35:40,140
Check my certificate.

888
00:35:40,140 --> 00:35:40,710
Mine too!

889
00:35:40,770 --> 00:35:42,290
-Look at mine first.
-Mr. Lyu,

890
00:35:42,290 --> 00:35:43,870
Huilong has been burned to the ground,

891
00:35:43,870 --> 00:35:45,080
yet they still honor
all withdrawal requests.

892
00:35:45,080 --> 00:35:46,060
Why does your bank

893
00:35:46,060 --> 00:35:47,600
only pay out 20% of deposits?

894
00:35:47,600 --> 00:35:48,860
That's unreasonable!

895
00:35:49,850 --> 00:35:50,600
What can I do?

896
00:35:51,310 --> 00:35:53,730
Mr. He Xian is too clever a businessman.

897
00:35:54,290 --> 00:35:56,660
He took advantage of the war
to undermine his industry peers.

898
00:35:56,660 --> 00:35:59,020
If I could stoop so low
as to make dirty money,

899
00:35:59,020 --> 00:35:59,810
I'd be doing what he's doing

900
00:35:59,810 --> 00:36:01,210
to make myself look good.

901
00:36:01,520 --> 00:36:02,330
Don't worry.

902
00:36:02,560 --> 00:36:05,290
I promise you'll get every cent back
from my bank.

903
00:36:05,640 --> 00:36:06,230
Yeah.

904
00:36:06,790 --> 00:36:08,450
In the future, Huilong will be

905
00:36:08,480 --> 00:36:10,140
the only golden brand left

906
00:36:10,140 --> 00:36:11,060
on the financial street.

907
00:36:11,060 --> 00:36:12,230
This is enough!

908
00:36:12,710 --> 00:36:13,450
You know what?

909
00:36:13,450 --> 00:36:14,430
To pay out all the deposits,

910
00:36:14,430 --> 00:36:16,090
-Xian even sold his...
-Quan!

911
00:36:17,160 --> 00:36:17,960
Focus on work.

912
00:36:24,830 --> 00:36:26,090
Is the amount correct?

913
00:36:27,500 --> 00:36:29,350
-Yes.
-I'll close your account then.

914
00:36:29,350 --> 00:36:29,960
Okay.

915
00:36:34,080 --> 00:36:34,770
Next!

916
00:36:38,690 --> 00:36:43,040
[December 24, 1941]

917
00:36:50,560 --> 00:36:52,490
Have all the depositors been paid?

918
00:36:54,310 --> 00:36:54,810
Yes.

919
00:36:55,850 --> 00:36:56,850
Good.

920
00:36:57,960 --> 00:37:01,430
The He family's reputation
is finally preserved.

921
00:37:02,210 --> 00:37:03,140
Kids,

922
00:37:03,140 --> 00:37:04,310
come eat!

923
00:37:04,680 --> 00:37:06,310
-Here I come!
-Here I come!

924
00:37:06,620 --> 00:37:07,680
Careful. It's hot.

925
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:12,740
Plain porridge again? I'm not eating it.

926
00:37:13,770 --> 00:37:14,780
Hey, you.

927
00:37:15,810 --> 00:37:16,540
Little Miss,

928
00:37:17,040 --> 00:37:18,750
a war's going on outside.

929
00:37:18,750 --> 00:37:21,230
Many people can't even have
thin rice gruel.

930
00:37:21,600 --> 00:37:22,280
Dear,

931
00:37:22,960 --> 00:37:24,930
tell Grandpa what you want to eat.

932
00:37:24,930 --> 00:37:26,770
It's Christmas Eve today.

933
00:37:26,770 --> 00:37:28,770
We eat apples on this day every year.

934
00:37:29,140 --> 00:37:29,910
Oh.

935
00:37:33,460 --> 00:37:35,190
Sis, let me tell you something.

936
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:39,850
Is it true?

937
00:37:40,230 --> 00:37:41,140
It is true.

938
00:37:41,140 --> 00:37:42,720
When have I ever lied to you?

939
00:37:42,890 --> 00:37:44,140
Eat the porridge now.

940
00:38:00,390 --> 00:38:01,370
Sir, you're back.

941
00:38:01,370 --> 00:38:01,930
Yes.

942
00:38:02,310 --> 00:38:03,240
Where is Yinwan?

943
00:38:04,450 --> 00:38:06,480
She was busy at the orphanage all day.

944
00:38:06,480 --> 00:38:07,350
Now,

945
00:38:07,830 --> 00:38:09,480
she's asleep on the sofa.

946
00:38:11,000 --> 00:38:12,400
Do we have any flour left?

947
00:38:13,040 --> 00:38:14,180
Flour?

948
00:38:14,180 --> 00:38:15,830
There should be a little bit left.

949
00:38:15,830 --> 00:38:16,270
Okay.

950
00:38:16,450 --> 00:38:17,960
As long as it's enough to make a pie.

951
00:38:17,960 --> 00:38:19,160
It won't be a problem.

952
00:38:19,850 --> 00:38:20,910
Huilong's crisis

953
00:38:21,500 --> 00:38:22,680
has been solved.

954
00:38:23,790 --> 00:38:25,500
We'd better leave soon.

955
00:38:26,600 --> 00:38:27,410
Where to?

956
00:38:27,410 --> 00:38:29,000
Isn't there only one choice?

957
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:29,850
Just listen.

958
00:38:30,080 --> 00:38:33,300
The sound of artillery
is coming from the Island non-stop.

959
00:38:33,300 --> 00:38:34,770
I think the British

960
00:38:35,270 --> 00:38:37,070
can only hold out for a day or two.

961
00:38:37,480 --> 00:38:39,100
Haven't you already applied

962
00:38:39,290 --> 00:38:41,950
for a license to operate
financial services in Macau?

963
00:38:41,950 --> 00:38:43,610
Once travel between Hong Kong

964
00:38:44,180 --> 00:38:46,140
and Macau resumes as the fire ceases,

965
00:38:46,140 --> 00:38:47,890
we should set off for Macau.

966
00:38:50,000 --> 00:38:50,730
Well,

967
00:38:51,210 --> 00:38:52,410
we'll see about that.

968
00:38:56,890 --> 00:38:57,350
Fine.

969
00:38:57,750 --> 00:38:59,180
Mull it over then.

970
00:39:09,270 --> 00:39:09,890
One,

971
00:39:09,890 --> 00:39:10,430
two,

972
00:39:10,430 --> 00:39:11,020
three,

973
00:39:11,020 --> 00:39:11,620
four,

974
00:39:11,620 --> 00:39:12,710
five...

975
00:39:12,710 --> 00:39:15,060
Five big apples.

976
00:39:15,230 --> 00:39:16,890
Why five?

977
00:39:16,890 --> 00:39:19,350
Because Grandpa, Dad,

978
00:39:19,350 --> 00:39:20,100
Mom,

979
00:39:20,100 --> 00:39:23,910
you, and I should each have one apple.

980
00:39:23,910 --> 00:39:24,960
That's right.

981
00:39:24,960 --> 00:39:26,450
But

982
00:39:26,450 --> 00:39:29,910
the apples in this drawing can't be eaten.

983
00:39:29,910 --> 00:39:31,250
Let me ask you.

984
00:39:31,250 --> 00:39:33,310
Why do we eat apples on Christmas Eve?

985
00:39:33,850 --> 00:39:35,310
That's the way

986
00:39:35,310 --> 00:39:37,340
we pray for safety.

987
00:39:38,100 --> 00:39:39,290
Then listen.

988
00:39:39,290 --> 00:39:40,680
As long as these are apples,

989
00:39:40,680 --> 00:39:42,290
be they in a painting

990
00:39:42,870 --> 00:39:44,310
or actually edible,

991
00:39:44,310 --> 00:39:46,250
they'll make our wish
for safety come true.

992
00:39:46,250 --> 00:39:47,710
Really?

993
00:39:48,730 --> 00:39:49,540
Is it sweet?

994
00:39:49,930 --> 00:39:50,730
Yes.

995
00:40:17,930 --> 00:40:18,730
What's wrong?

996
00:40:19,290 --> 00:40:20,890
Is something bothering you?

997
00:40:24,020 --> 00:40:26,950
Are there depositors
who haven't made withdrawals?

998
00:40:29,600 --> 00:40:30,680
All the depositors

999
00:40:31,210 --> 00:40:32,740
have received their money,

1000
00:40:33,290 --> 00:40:34,980
except our biggest client,

1001
00:40:35,270 --> 00:40:36,670
who deposited a large sum

1002
00:40:37,540 --> 00:40:39,000
and requested anonymity.

1003
00:40:40,450 --> 00:40:41,830
Since that was a special case,

1004
00:40:41,830 --> 00:40:43,890
I made a note about him on the last page

1005
00:40:44,080 --> 00:40:46,660
for differentiation
from the other depositors.

1006
00:40:46,660 --> 00:40:48,460
Though the last page was burned,

1007
00:40:49,040 --> 00:40:51,750
I vividly remember his face and the amount

1008
00:40:52,790 --> 00:40:53,930
of his deposit.

1009
00:40:56,500 --> 00:40:57,370
How much?

1010
00:40:58,120 --> 00:40:58,830
A bit

1011
00:40:59,910 --> 00:41:00,910
more than 30,000.

1012
00:41:06,250 --> 00:41:07,250
That is to say,

1013
00:41:08,680 --> 00:41:10,810
if this client withdraws his deposit,

1014
00:41:10,930 --> 00:41:12,330
we'll be left penniless.

1015
00:41:15,290 --> 00:41:16,580
It's been over 10 days.

1016
00:41:17,080 --> 00:41:18,680
I don't know why he hasn't

1017
00:41:18,680 --> 00:41:19,520
shown up yet.

1018
00:41:20,390 --> 00:41:21,390
I also have no idea

1019
00:41:21,580 --> 00:41:23,810
whether he'll come
to get this money or not.

1020
00:41:23,810 --> 00:41:24,710
But Huilong

1021
00:41:25,660 --> 00:41:26,860
won't stop providing

1022
00:41:27,450 --> 00:41:29,580
withdrawal service until tomorrow.

1023
00:41:56,460 --> 00:41:57,660
Merry Christmas Eve.

1024
00:41:58,330 --> 00:41:59,160
Merry Christmas Eve,

1025
00:41:59,160 --> 00:41:59,850
Renyu.

1026
00:42:01,830 --> 00:42:03,230
Freshly baked apple pie.

1027
00:42:03,250 --> 00:42:03,950
Eat up.

1028
00:42:05,580 --> 00:42:06,440
This is for you.

1029
00:42:07,290 --> 00:42:09,090
Grabbing with your hands again?

1030
00:42:24,600 --> 00:42:26,210
This reminds me of the past.

1031
00:42:26,980 --> 00:42:28,640
When you were only 7 years old,

1032
00:42:29,060 --> 00:42:30,720
you devoured a large apple pie

1033
00:42:31,020 --> 00:42:32,700
all at once.

1034
00:42:32,700 --> 00:42:34,480
The priest and the housemother
were shocked.

1035
00:42:34,480 --> 00:42:35,890
I was starving.

1036
00:42:35,890 --> 00:42:37,230
I hadn't eaten all day.

1037
00:42:37,480 --> 00:42:38,740
On every Christmas Eve

1038
00:42:38,960 --> 00:42:40,390
after that day, the housemother

1039
00:42:40,390 --> 00:42:42,680
would make an apple pie
specifically for you,

1040
00:42:42,680 --> 00:42:45,010
regardless of what was served for dinner.

1041
00:42:45,600 --> 00:42:47,730
Then we grew up and left the orphanage.

1042
00:42:48,180 --> 00:42:51,040
You became the one
making me an apple pie every year.

1043
00:42:51,680 --> 00:42:53,880
On each and every future Christmas Eve,

1044
00:42:54,620 --> 00:42:55,710
I will always

1045
00:42:56,480 --> 00:42:58,770
make you an apple pie right on time.
